this was flagging so i made a good one that doesn't flag if you hold second keybind used for palcing :)

 module double-crystal
def desc Double crystal (might be working auto d tap)

on tick if input_active use if holding #crystal if target_entity :end_crystal then wait_random 0.1 0.3 then input left then input right then wait 0.05 then input left